Package: puRephd
Type: Package
Title: Automate Creation and Update of PhD Theses in PURE
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("David Nicolas", "Matzig", role = c("aut","cre"), email = "dnma@kb.dk")
Description: Modular tools to ingest data about awarded PhDs, reconcile with internal persons
    and organizations, and create or update PhD thesis-meta data in PURE via its REST API.
    Provides a single high-level workflow plus composable steps.
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
